<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/faq.css">
    <title>Recipe Sharing - FAQ</title>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Include the header here -->
    <%- include("header.ejs") %>

    <div class="faq-container">
        <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">How can I submit my recipe?</button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>You can submit your recipe by navigating to the "Submit Recipe" section from the main menu. Fill out the form with all necessary details including ingredients, steps, and images.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">Do I need an account to submit a recipe?</button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>Yes, you need to create an account or log in to submit a recipe. This helps us to credit the right person and manage the recipes effectively.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">Can I edit or delete my submitted recipe?</button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>Yes, you can edit or delete your submitted recipe from your account dashboard. Go to "My Recipes" and select the recipe you want to edit or delete.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">How do I search for specific recipes?</button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>You can use the search bar at the top of the page to search for specific recipes. You can filter your search by ingredients, cuisine, or recipe name.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">Are the recipes verified for accuracy?</button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>We do our best to verify the recipes for accuracy, but we recommend reading user reviews and comments for additional insights.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">Can I rate and review recipes?</button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>Yes, you can rate and review recipes. Your feedback helps other users and improves the quality of our community.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">How can I contact support?</button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>If you need any help or have questions, please use the "Contact Us" form available in the menu. Our support team will get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Include the Footer here -->
    
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Recipe Oasis. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="scripts/faq.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
